OL,3,CEx-Reform UK council leader resigns
OL,4,Cover alleged racist comments
OL,6,FIan Cooper has resigned as leader of
OL,7,FStaffordshire County Council, stepping
OL,8,Fdown just days after Reform UK revoked
OL,9,Fhis party membership over allegations
OL,10,Fhe posted racist comments on social
OL,11,Fmedia.
OL,13,FThe party announced on Friday that Mr
OL,14,FCooper had been removed following what
OL,15,Fit described as "an investigation into
OL,16,Fthe failure to declare social media
OL,17,Faccounts during the candidate vetting
OL,18,Fprocess".
