OL,3,CEx-Reform UK council leader resigns
OL,4,Cover alleged racist comments
OL,6,FActing leader Councillor Martin Murray
OL,7,Fhas said that Staffordshire must
OL,8,Fremain a place that "represents all
OL,9,Fresidents fairly and with respect."
OL,11,FCllr Murray said: "I recognise that
OL,12,Fthese are challenging circumstances
OL,13,Fand the strength of feeling
OL,14,Fsurrounding recent events.
OL,16,F"Let me assure you that my commitment
OL,17,Fto deliver plans for a better
OL,18,FStaffordshire remains absolute, and to
OL,19,Frepresent all residents fairly and
OL,20,Fwith respect.
