OL,6,FMr Cooper is also alleged to have
OL,7,Fposted a comment about the black,
OL,8,FBritish-born lawyer and activist Shola
OL,9,FMos-Shogbamimu, saying "Dr Shaga Bing-
OL,10,FBong.... Time she F'd off back to
OL,11,FNigeria. She'd feel more at home
OL,12,Fthere."
