OL,3,CEx-Reform UK council leader resigns
OL,4,Cover alleged racist comments
OL,6,FMr Cooper's resignation follows
OL,7,Fmounting political pressure and a
OL,8,Fpublic row sparked by remarks he made
OL,9,Fonline in response to criticism from
OL,10,FTamworth's Labour MP Sarah Edwards.
OL,12,FMP Edwards said the conduct of Reform
OL,13,FUK councillors in Staffordshire was
OL,14,F"deeply concerning", and criticised
OL,15,Fwhat she called "deafening" silence
OL,16,Ffrom Mr Cooper's colleagues regarding
OL,17,Fthe allegations.
