OL,3,CEx-Reform UK council leader resigns
OL,4,Cover alleged racist comments
OL,6,F"In a statement, she said: "So far,
OL,7,Fhis colleagues have not condemned this
OL,8,Fbehaviour or these views. If this
OL,9,Fconduct is reflective of the county's
OL,10,Fleadership, it raises serious
OL,11,Fquestions about the standards and
OL,12,Fvalues of Ian Cooper's colleagues."
OL,14,FMr Cooper responded directly on her
OL,15,FFacebook page, insisting she was
OL,16,F"wrong on so many levels" and
OL,17,Fdismissing her concerns about wider
OL,18,Fissues within the local Reform group.
OL,19,FHis comments escalated into a brief
OL,20,Fexchange before he stopped posting
OL,21,Fpublicly.
