OL,3,CEx-Reform UK council leader resigns
OL,4,Cover alleged racist comments
OL,6,FDespite Mr Cooper pushing back at MP
OL,7,FEdwards' remarks, he has not publicly
OL,8,Faddressed the posts he is alleged to
OL,9,Fhave made earlier this year.
OL,11,FHope Not Hate claims the comments
OL,12,Ftargeted several public figures and
OL,13,Fincluded racist language.
OL,15,FThe council has said its priority is
OL,16,Fto ensure continuity of services
OL,17,F"without disruption". Mr Cooper
OL,18,Fremains an elected councillor for
OL,19,FTamworth.
